default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultIn South Wales, there is the Community Intensive Therapy Team (CITT), which is aimed at young people who need more support than that usually provided in outpatient settings.
default This service reduced the need to admit young people to inpatien
defaultt units, and between 2001-2006 
defaultthere were n
defaulto referrals 
defaultto Tier
default 4 
defaultservices (
defaultinpatient services and other highly specialist provision) outside of the region. http://www.bmj.com/rapid-response/2011/10/31/community-intensive-therapy-team
default 
defaultThere is also the Fife Intensive Therapy Team, which uses a similar service model, which sees young people in their homes or in a suitable community facility. This service has also been shown to be effective in improving young people’s menta
defaultl health.
default6.2.
default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultMany young people prefer to access 
defaultvoluntary sector
default services as they are often on the high street
default and are less stigmatising
default.
default 
defaultFor instance, 
defaultYouth, Information, Advice and Counselling Services (YIACS) offer a range of different
default services under one roof. Research has found that the young people accessing these services have very high levels of mental illness (Youth
default 
defaultAccess, 2012).
default YIACs have different configurations including counselling services, sexual health, drugs advice etc, but
default The Zone 
defaultin Plymouth - http://www.thezoneplymouth.co.uk/ offers a range of services including access to an early
default intervention psychosis service
default, and a service for young people with emerging personality disorders.
